# 母親是否為軍公教

mcareer[mcareer8 == 2|mcareer8 == 3|mcareer8 == 4|mcareer8 == 5|mcareer8 == 6|mcareer8 == 7|mcareer8 == 8] <- 0
# 雙親任一者為軍公教
